&lt;h1&gt;Staff Nurse Discharge Planning&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a qualified post within the discharge planning team. We are looking for an innovative and dynamic nurse with proven experience and skills in discharge planning. They will join a growing and enthusiastic team offering professional advice to patients, carers and colleagues in regards to the discharge planning process at PHU. We strive to improve the experience of the patients journey through strong discharge support, ensuring that the patients wishes are at the centre of care being being offered to them. You will have the chance to liaise and work with multiple professional agencies within the role. The focus of the Discharge Planning Team is to support the complexities of patients to ensure a timely and appropriate discharge takes place. There will be opportunities to develop your knowledge within this role. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date 23rd November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
